{"tid":2381883,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【獨家】彭定康聯同一眾MP趁住香港開埠一百八十周年向港人送上鼓勵！","createTime":"2021-01-27T02:13:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T08:33:47.000Z","uid":273297,"like":39,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b7aa7309bf6f9924cf3921cb40c6361cb23648cd","tid":2381883,"uid":273297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T02:13:13.000Z","msg":"適逢尋日係香港開埠紀念，重光團隊為咗聊表心意，特意準備咗一份賀禮送俾香港 &mdash; 有幸邀請到<strong><span class=\"blue\">前港督彭定康勳爵聯同位十二位英國國會議員同埋人權倡議人仕</span></strong>，喺呢個咁有意義嘅日子為港人送上祝福同鼓勵！本身諗住噚日就擺上嚟，但由於反應熱烈，陸陸續續有 MP send 片嚟俾我哋，所以儲埋一次過而家先出，希望大家鍾意啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPart 1<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YjVdluA-TLU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYjVdluA-TLU&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSv%2BgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=37df0418\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YjVdluA-TLU</a><br />\n<br />\nPart 2<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XkzAPn__nH8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXkzAPn__nH8&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSv%2BgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=968f62f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XkzAPn__nH8</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除左以上嘅打氣片之外，<strong><span class=\"blue\">我哋亦都搵左 Andrew Rosindell MP 喺下議院發起咗個 Early Day Motion</span></strong>，講述香港開埠一百八十周年嘅歷史意義，重申香港同英國兩地嘅歷史聯繫，並繼續鼓勵英國政府同朝野各黨繼續支持同歡迎香港人。身在英國嘅朋友可以聯絡你嘅 MP 去邀請佢哋表態支持：<a href=\"https://edm.parliament.uk/early-day-motion/57987\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedm.parliament.uk%2Fearly-day-motion%2F57987&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSv%2BgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=ce1124fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://edm.parliament.uk/early-day-motion/57987</a><br />\n<br />\n香港呢一百八十年走來不易，尤其過去廿多年香港人更加經歷咗唔少辛酸。如彭督所言，香港人非常珍惜自由嘅價值，唔會輕易放棄。否極泰來，願榮光歸香港之時，我哋能夠攜手踏上另一個歷史里程碑。<br />\n<br />\n重光團隊除左舉辦呢類同香港歷史文化有關嘅活動，喺海外構建香港民族共識之外，我哋亦繼續同擴展國際戰線。通過既有以及我哋近幾個月新建立緊嘅政界關係，我哋會喺唔同渠道推動英國及歐盟作出更多<strong><span class=\"blue\">支持港人同懲罰中共嘅實際行動</span></strong>，包括：定期與各國議員及相關組織會面，遊說各國盡快制裁中港官員、推行廣泛金融制裁、叫停《歐中投資協議》、同抵制中共滲透等等。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"blue\">感謝英國與港人同行，<br />\n共同紀念香港開埠日</span></strong> 🎂<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 如果手足想要睇中文字幕既話，麻煩係YouTube字幕設定入面揀我哋團隊為你哋準備好嘅廣東話字幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FACXeya.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFACXeya.png&h=034c0b51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<strong>其他社交媒體專頁同網站</strong><br />\nYoutube:<br />\n<a href=\"http://youtube.com/standwithhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fstandwithhk&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSv%2BgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=ef879c4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">youtube.com/standwithhk</a><br />\nTwitter:<br />\n<a href=\"http://twitter.com/Stand_with_HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FStand_with_HK&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSv%2BgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=ba9cc154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">twitter.com/Stand_with_HK</a><br />\nFacebook:<br />\n<a href=\"http://facebook.com/standwithhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Fstandwithhk&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSv%2BgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=7ea2b1cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">facebook.com/standwithhk</a><br />\nIG:<br />\n<a href=\"http://instagram.com/standwithhk_\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fstandwithhk_&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSv%2BgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=66bb8cec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">instagram.com/standwithhk_</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n重光團隊 SWHK Channel 🏴:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/FFFSWHK20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FFFFSWHK20&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSv%2BgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=cd97383e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/FFFSWHK20</a>"},{"pid":"4464c909d57f374720bef6aeaadd1609a094f022","tid":2381883,"uid":273297,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T02:13:25.000Z","msg":"如果想多謝彭督同咁多位撐香港嘅英國議員，就請上我哋嘅 Twitter 留個言啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋一齊逐一同佢哋講聲多謝：<br />\n<br />\nThe Lord Patten of Barnes 前港督彭定康勳爵 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Stand_with_HK/status/1354073312620670980\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FStand_with_HK%2Fstatus%2F1354073312620670980&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSv%2BgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=e560d32e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FStand_with_HK%2Fstatus%2F1354073312620670980&h=6fbf4d9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Stand_with_HK/status/1354073312620670980</a><br />\nSir Iain Duncan Smith MP 施志安爵士<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Stand_with_HK/status/1354077285981286402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FStand_with_HK%2Fstatus%2F1354077285981286402&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSv%2BgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=0484c617\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FStand_with_HK%2Fstatus%2F1354077285981286402&h=6f52692d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Stand_with_HK/status/1354077285981286402</a><br />\nVirendra Sharma MP 沙馬斐議員<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Stand_with_HK/status/1354081157676212224\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FStand_with_HK%2Fstatus%2F1354081157676212224&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSv%2BgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=24b50e64\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FStand_with_HK%2Fstatus%2F1354081157676212224&h=5dd83c22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Stand_with_HK/status/1354081157676212224</a><br />\nSir David Amess MP 安默使爵士<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Stand_with_HK